WEBVTT

00:01:00.960 --> 00:01:01.719
Thank you

00:01:03.520 --> 00:01:05.519
Don't shoulder everything by yourself

00:01:06.319 --> 00:01:07.239
Occasionally, let your sisters

00:01:07.239 --> 00:01:08.840
be your emotional trash can

00:01:12.040 --> 00:01:12.959
Thank you, guys

00:01:14.480 --> 00:01:15.359
It's only here with us

00:01:15.359 --> 00:01:16.680
that you can vent a little

00:01:17.840 --> 00:01:19.239
You can't cry to Xiaocan,

00:01:20.040 --> 00:01:21.159
can't cry to Gui Fang,

00:01:22.280 --> 00:01:23.640
and feel bad crying at home

00:01:24.879 --> 00:01:26.480
It's a minefield everywhere

00:01:27.280 --> 00:01:28.120
My heart aches for you

00:01:31.439 --> 00:01:32.840
I know crying is useless

00:01:34.239 --> 00:01:35.280
and a waste of time

00:01:37.239 --> 00:01:38.040
But Xiaocan...

00:01:39.280 --> 00:01:40.480
his remaining time

00:01:41.760 --> 00:01:43.519
is ticking away second by second

00:01:45.680 --> 00:01:47.319
And I can't do anything about it

00:01:49.519 --> 00:01:50.239
All things considered,

00:01:51.519 --> 00:01:52.680
Xiaocan's time...

00:01:54.120 --> 00:01:55.319
there's only a week left, right?

00:01:56.719 --> 00:01:57.319
Eight days

00:01:59.959 --> 00:02:00.879
At the very most,

00:02:02.719 --> 00:02:03.879
there are eight days left

00:02:07.599 --> 00:02:08.680
Then for the remaining days,

00:02:09.840 --> 00:02:11.120
let's spend more time with Xiaocan

00:02:12.599 --> 00:02:14.400
It's good to leave him with more happy memories

00:02:18.520 --> 00:02:19.639
But I think

00:02:20.639 --> 00:02:22.560
Godmother probably needs Xiaocan's company more

00:02:24.719 --> 00:02:25.800
There are only a few days left

00:02:26.439 --> 00:02:27.840
It's better to leave Xiaocan's time

00:02:28.719 --> 00:02:29.680
for Godmother

00:02:35.439 --> 00:02:36.319
In these last few days,

00:02:38.520 --> 00:02:39.520
whether it's Xiaocan

00:02:40.280 --> 00:02:40.960
or us,

00:02:42.280 --> 00:02:43.560
we must live happily

00:02:44.159 --> 00:02:44.479
Right

00:02:45.439 --> 00:02:46.280
Live happily

00:02:47.919 --> 00:02:48.800
Live happily

00:02:49.800 --> 00:02:50.520
I'm okay now

00:02:51.719 --> 00:02:52.039
Live

00:02:55.599 --> 00:02:58.240
I'm not okay

00:03:08.680 --> 00:03:11.479
These seedlings are what you planted a while back

00:03:11.680 --> 00:03:12.719
Now they've grown this big

00:03:13.080 --> 00:03:14.319
After you take them back,

00:03:14.560 --> 00:03:16.919
pay attention to their growth marks

00:03:17.000 --> 00:03:18.159
Record them down

00:03:18.439 --> 00:03:20.639
You must cherish your experimental results

00:03:20.639 --> 00:03:21.319
Got it?

00:03:21.479 --> 00:03:22.120
Got it

00:03:22.240 --> 00:03:23.479
Take them, take them, quick

00:03:24.479 --> 00:03:24.919
You take this one

00:03:25.000 --> 00:03:25.719
This one, this one grew well

00:03:27.639 --> 00:03:27.919
Okay

00:03:35.800 --> 00:03:36.159
Mom

00:03:36.680 --> 00:03:38.919
Come to Wanxiang Denong this afternoon to help clean up the mess?

00:03:40.879 --> 00:03:41.680
Mom is busy

00:03:41.960 --> 00:03:42.759
Ask Xu Rui

00:03:42.840 --> 00:03:43.800
Let her help you clean up

00:03:46.120 --> 00:03:48.680
Better leave more time for Xiaocan and Xu Rui

00:03:55.159 --> 00:03:55.599
Xu Rui

00:03:55.919 --> 00:03:56.879
The key points I highlighted...

00:03:57.039 --> 00:03:58.000
review them carefully

00:03:58.960 --> 00:03:59.560
Okay, Coach

00:04:00.080 --> 00:04:00.800
I'm going to a meeting now

00:04:09.000 --> 00:04:09.479
Rui Rui

00:04:09.759 --> 00:04:11.879
Come to Wanxiang Denong this afternoon to help clean up the mess?

00:04:16.240 --> 00:04:17.279
I'm busy getting my certification

00:04:17.800 --> 00:04:19.160
There's not enough time

00:04:19.959 --> 00:04:20.959
Go ask Auntie

00:04:21.240 --> 00:04:22.360
See if she has time to help you

00:04:26.720 --> 00:04:29.319
Better leave more time for Xiaocan and Auntie

00:04:37.839 --> 00:04:38.240
Boss

00:04:39.000 --> 00:04:39.680
I have a question

00:04:40.360 --> 00:04:41.839
Do I get paid?

00:04:42.160 --> 00:04:42.720
Don't worry

00:04:43.759 --> 00:04:45.120
Renting this small warehouse

00:04:45.279 --> 00:04:47.279
is the first step for our shop to take off

00:04:47.639 --> 00:04:48.560
When we get to the second step

00:04:48.959 --> 00:04:50.240
and actually take off,

00:04:50.839 --> 00:04:51.720
you definitely won't be left out

00:04:53.000 --> 00:04:53.399
Good

00:04:54.079 --> 00:04:55.120
So, no wages then

00:04:56.480 --> 00:04:56.920
Fair enough

00:04:57.160 --> 00:04:58.319
As the old saying goes:

00:04:58.920 --> 00:04:59.920
A tree lives for its bark,

00:05:00.160 --> 00:05:01.120
a man lives for a flatbread

00:05:01.600 --> 00:05:02.720
Cut the crap, get to work

00:05:03.120 --> 00:05:03.639
Alright

00:05:07.120 --> 00:05:07.560
Bro

00:05:07.959 --> 00:05:09.839
Come to Wanxiang Denong this afternoon to help clean up the mess?

00:05:10.680 --> 00:05:11.040
Xiao Yin

00:05:12.600 --> 00:05:13.000
Xiaocan

00:05:23.399 --> 00:05:24.319
Sorry, bro.

00:05:24.439 --> 00:05:25.879
I'm packing with Sister Yin right now.

00:05:25.920 --> 00:05:26.600
Let's go another day.

00:05:32.920 --> 00:05:33.920
Bad timing, bro.

00:05:33.920 --> 00:05:35.480
I'm busy packing right now, I don't have...

00:05:42.079 --> 00:05:43.240
No, why don't you just text me?

00:05:48.319 --> 00:05:49.439
Do we really not need to go over there?

00:05:53.399 --> 00:05:54.240
There are only a few days left.

00:05:54.920 --> 00:05:56.720
Better leave the time for Godmother and Sister Rui.

00:06:30.240 --> 00:06:32.079
Mom, can you come keep me company?

00:06:32.079 --> 00:06:33.959
My time is running out.

00:06:33.959 --> 00:06:35.759
Come keep me company, Mom.

00:06:35.759 --> 00:06:36.879
Mom, I'm begging you.

00:06:37.399 --> 00:06:38.480
Li Wai, are you even human?

00:06:38.879 --> 00:06:39.800
Look at the state I'm in right now.

00:06:39.800 --> 00:06:40.759
You won't come? You won't come?

00:06:41.199 --> 00:06:42.399
You... You have to come!

00:06:42.839 --> 00:06:43.639
Xu Rui.

00:06:44.560 --> 00:06:46.399
I can't make it... I really can't make it.

00:06:46.560 --> 00:06:47.639
I really need you.

00:06:47.639 --> 00:06:49.360
I'm begging you.

00:06:49.360 --> 00:06:50.439
Come see me, quick.

00:06:50.439 --> 00:06:51.920
I really can't make it. Darn it.

00:06:54.920 --> 00:06:56.360
Oh my god.

00:07:11.879 --> 00:07:12.360
Professor Wang.

00:07:12.759 --> 00:07:13.360
I need to take some time off.

00:07:14.879 --> 00:07:15.319
What are you doing?

00:07:18.319 --> 00:07:18.639
Okay.

00:07:28.800 --> 00:07:29.279
Xiaocan.

00:07:30.959 --> 00:07:31.360
Xiaocan.

00:07:37.399 --> 00:07:38.079
What are you doing?

00:07:39.279 --> 00:07:40.439
I really can't piece it together.

00:07:40.439 --> 00:07:41.879
I'll just give it my head.

00:07:42.319 --> 00:07:44.000
None of you came to keep me company.

00:07:44.279 --> 00:07:44.519
Well...

00:07:45.360 --> 00:07:46.839
Why are you here all alone?

00:07:47.079 --> 00:07:47.720
Where are the others?

00:07:47.920 --> 00:07:50.120
None of them came to keep me company.

00:07:50.399 --> 00:07:51.000
Xiaocan.

00:07:51.399 --> 00:07:51.959
Xiaocan.

00:07:54.240 --> 00:07:55.600
Little Rui, why are you here alone?

00:07:56.399 --> 00:07:57.040
Where is Xiaocan?

00:08:01.240 --> 00:08:01.560
No...

00:08:02.160 --> 00:08:03.000
What are you doing?

00:08:03.120 --> 00:08:04.120
I can't piece it together.

00:08:04.120 --> 00:08:05.519
I gave it my head.

00:08:05.759 --> 00:08:08.120
None of you came to keep me company.

00:08:08.399 --> 00:08:09.480
Isn't Little Rui right here?

00:08:10.079 --> 00:08:11.000
I just got here.

00:08:12.439 --> 00:08:13.800
I thought you were with him the whole time.

00:08:15.480 --> 00:08:16.040
Bro.

00:08:16.519 --> 00:08:17.040
Bro.

00:08:17.240 --> 00:08:18.240
I'm here, bro.

00:08:18.600 --> 00:08:19.000
Xiaocan.

00:08:19.000 --> 00:08:19.439
Bro.

00:08:20.560 --> 00:08:21.680
Godmother, Sister Rui.

00:08:22.680 --> 00:08:23.279
Where is Xiaocan?

00:08:26.360 --> 00:08:27.839
Bro, why have you mutated?

00:08:27.839 --> 00:08:29.800
I couldn't piece the head together, so I gave it my head.

00:08:29.959 --> 00:08:31.959
None of you came to keep me company.

00:08:32.080 --> 00:08:33.559
Aren't Godmother and Sister Rui keeping you company?

00:08:34.759 --> 00:08:35.799
We just got here.

00:08:37.120 --> 00:08:37.840
You two just got here too?

00:08:39.440 --> 00:08:41.279
So... so nobody came to keep you company?

00:08:41.960 --> 00:08:43.039
I was thinking of leaving the time...

00:08:43.039 --> 00:08:44.399
...all to you and Xu Rui.

00:08:45.159 --> 00:08:48.159
I was thinking of leaving the time for you and Auntie.

00:08:48.919 --> 00:08:51.039
We thought we'd leave the time for you guys.

00:08:51.240 --> 00:08:53.240
Isn't this just like The Gift of the Magi?

00:08:53.519 --> 00:08:54.240
You thought, you thought.

00:08:54.240 --> 00:08:55.720
Did no one ask what I thought?

00:08:55.919 --> 00:08:56.480
It was a misunderstanding.

00:08:58.639 --> 00:08:59.039
Bro.

00:09:00.440 --> 00:09:01.279
It's all my fault.

00:09:02.120 --> 00:09:02.480
How about this.

00:09:03.679 --> 00:09:04.480
To make it up to you...

00:09:05.360 --> 00:09:06.320
...come stay at my place tonight.

00:09:06.919 --> 00:09:08.000
Let's party all night long.

00:09:17.039 --> 00:09:17.440
Bro.

00:09:18.679 --> 00:09:19.120
Let me ask you.

00:09:20.440 --> 00:09:21.039
Are you scared?

00:09:24.120 --> 00:09:24.519
I am.

00:09:25.759 --> 00:09:26.159
Li Wai.

00:09:27.600 --> 00:09:28.480
After I'm gone...

00:09:29.039 --> 00:09:30.240
...you must take good care of my mom.

00:09:30.840 --> 00:09:32.240
Take care of her like she's your own mother.

00:09:32.639 --> 00:09:33.720
Don't worry.

00:09:33.720 --> 00:09:35.039
I will definitely take good care of Godmother.

00:09:35.039 --> 00:09:36.600
She's as dear to me as my own mother.

00:09:37.200 --> 00:09:37.720
That's good then.

00:09:39.360 --> 00:09:39.879
Bro.

00:09:40.879 --> 00:09:41.399
So...

00:09:42.240 --> 00:09:44.039
Do you have any unfulfilled wishes left?

00:09:48.480 --> 00:09:48.840
None.

00:09:49.879 --> 00:09:50.600
My life was worth it.

00:09:52.960 --> 00:09:53.320
Let's sleep.

00:10:01.159 --> 00:10:01.559
Sleep.

00:10:22.960 --> 00:10:23.480
Coming.

00:10:28.360 --> 00:10:28.759
Gui Fang.

00:10:28.879 --> 00:10:29.320
Xiao Tian.

00:10:29.440 --> 00:10:30.480
Brother Xiaocan asked me to come.

00:10:30.840 --> 00:10:32.159
Is there anything here you need help with?

00:10:34.000 --> 00:10:35.159
This afternoon, Brother Xiaocan told me...

00:10:35.480 --> 00:10:36.799
...to go help him out.

00:10:37.320 --> 00:10:38.519
I was busy with mapping and surveying.

00:10:38.519 --> 00:10:39.960
So I didn't check my phone and didn't go.

00:10:40.240 --> 00:10:41.840
He just told me to come to your place to see...

00:10:42.120 --> 00:10:43.639
...if there's anything I can help with, just ask.

00:10:48.200 --> 00:10:49.080
Next time...

00:10:49.200 --> 00:10:50.399
...if you have your own things to do...

00:10:50.399 --> 00:10:51.600
...just focus on your side first.

00:10:51.919 --> 00:10:52.480
Have you eaten?

00:10:53.039 --> 00:10:53.720
Not yet.

00:10:54.200 --> 00:10:54.679
Then come on in.

00:11:01.279 --> 00:11:02.360
Wasn't I coming to work?

00:11:03.360 --> 00:11:04.720
I've finished all the housework.

00:11:04.720 --> 00:11:05.360
There's nothing left to do.

00:11:05.879 --> 00:11:06.240
Just eat.

00:11:16.200 --> 00:11:17.080
By the way, Xiao Tian.

00:11:17.480 --> 00:11:19.240
Have you played with that Lego?

00:11:19.960 --> 00:11:20.399
Lego?

00:11:21.559 --> 00:11:22.200
I haven't played with it.

00:11:23.200 --> 00:11:24.320
That seems pretty fun.

00:11:27.759 --> 00:11:28.600
It is indeed pretty fun.

00:11:30.080 --> 00:11:31.320
Xiaocan just loves playing with this.

00:11:32.919 --> 00:11:35.559
Nowadays adults have more toys than kids do.

00:11:36.279 --> 00:11:36.799
It seems...

00:11:37.240 --> 00:11:38.279
...no one wants to be an adult.

00:11:39.320 --> 00:11:40.639
Everyone wants to stay a child forever...

00:11:41.159 --> 00:11:42.120
...and keep playing with toys.

00:11:50.679 --> 00:11:51.679
I always feel like...

00:11:53.399 --> 00:11:55.080
...Xiaocan is still that...

00:11:56.200 --> 00:11:57.919
...little kid who loves playing with toys.

00:12:04.440 --> 00:12:05.320
Just this big.

00:12:11.200 --> 00:12:12.039
In the blink of an eye...

00:12:13.919 --> 00:12:14.639
...he's grown so tall.

00:12:22.360 --> 00:12:23.200
You guys...

00:12:24.840 --> 00:12:26.240
...will all grow up more.

00:12:27.720 --> 00:12:28.559
And get older.

00:12:34.799 --> 00:12:36.039
But my Xiaocan...

00:12:40.639 --> 00:12:41.759
...will stay this age forever.

00:12:58.720 --> 00:12:59.240
Gui Fang.

00:13:02.120 --> 00:13:02.840
Actually, I...

00:13:03.399 --> 00:13:04.480
...am really afraid of saying the wrong thing.

00:13:05.360 --> 00:13:06.720
Especially anything related to death.

00:13:08.960 --> 00:13:09.679
But don't worry.

00:13:11.000 --> 00:13:12.279
I will always be by your side.

00:13:21.799 --> 00:13:22.799
Eat up, eat up.

00:13:23.320 --> 00:13:24.000
While it's hot.

00:14:15.000 --> 00:14:15.559
Mom.

00:14:16.159 --> 00:14:17.639
Do people die?

00:14:18.000 --> 00:14:19.120
Will you die too?

00:14:19.519 --> 00:14:20.759
Will I die too?

00:14:21.559 --> 00:14:23.159
Cartoons are all lies.

00:14:23.559 --> 00:14:24.440
We won't die.

00:14:24.559 --> 00:14:25.080
Mom.

00:14:25.639 --> 00:14:26.799
If you die...

00:14:27.240 --> 00:14:28.960
...I'll go die with you.

00:14:30.960 --> 00:14:32.399
Okay, okay, die together.

00:14:34.440 --> 00:14:34.919
Touch wood.

00:14:35.240 --> 00:14:36.759
What... what is this talk about dying?

00:14:36.919 --> 00:14:37.679
We're not dying.

00:14:40.080 --> 00:14:42.279
Why do these cartoons scare children?

00:15:26.519 --> 00:15:26.960
Bro.

00:15:27.639 --> 00:15:28.960
Stop sleeping! Get up, get up!

00:15:29.360 --> 00:15:30.159
You're about to die!

00:15:30.159 --> 00:15:31.360
How do you still have time to sleep?

00:15:31.480 --> 00:15:32.600
Quick, quick, quick! Get up!

00:15:33.600 --> 00:15:35.159
Sister Rui has her Referee Certification written exam today.

00:15:35.840 --> 00:15:36.879
Aren't you going to bring her food?

00:15:38.360 --> 00:15:39.879
I... Right, I'm going.

00:15:42.440 --> 00:15:42.840
Bro.

00:15:43.320 --> 00:15:43.840
Let me tell you.

00:15:44.279 --> 00:15:45.440
Last night after you fell asleep...

00:15:45.960 --> 00:15:47.120
...I looked at you and thought for a long time.

00:15:49.039 --> 00:15:50.039
You're dying soon.

00:15:50.360 --> 00:15:51.720
There's still so much we haven't done together.

00:15:52.279 --> 00:15:53.039
That...

00:15:53.919 --> 00:15:54.639
...isn't appropriate.

00:15:55.000 --> 00:15:55.399
The two of us...

00:15:55.919 --> 00:15:57.080
Bro, no need for that, I...

00:15:57.080 --> 00:15:57.960
I chose all of these.

00:15:58.480 --> 00:15:59.799
Pick one and we'll go do it right now.

00:16:06.799 --> 00:16:08.279
What the hell is this "spending Valentine's Day together"?

00:16:08.279 --> 00:16:08.679
Don't worry about that.

00:16:08.679 --> 00:16:09.519
I... I'm going to deliver food first.

00:16:09.679 --> 00:16:11.080
No, pick one, Can.

00:16:12.159 --> 00:16:12.480
Can.

00:16:16.720 --> 00:16:18.120
I... I brought you a lunch made with love.

00:16:18.120 --> 00:16:18.840
It's all your favorites.

00:16:19.200 --> 00:16:19.879
Remember to eat it.

00:16:20.360 --> 00:16:21.159
How... how did your exam go?

00:16:21.720 --> 00:16:22.799
Based on my experience with CET-4 and CET-6,

00:16:22.919 --> 00:16:23.720
Health Manager,

00:16:23.720 --> 00:16:24.440
Public Nutritionist,

00:16:24.480 --> 00:16:25.840
and Computer Rank Examination certificates,

00:16:25.879 --> 00:16:26.360
it shouldn't be a problem.

00:16:26.759 --> 00:16:27.679
Seeing you like this puts me at ease.

00:16:27.879 --> 00:16:28.159
I'm off.

00:16:28.799 --> 00:16:29.080
Okay.

00:16:30.000 --> 00:16:30.320
Xu Rui.

00:16:30.919 --> 00:16:31.919
The thing you always forget...

00:16:31.919 --> 00:16:33.159
The Zero False Start rule

00:16:33.279 --> 00:16:34.679
started on August 12, 2009,

00:16:34.679 --> 00:16:36.000
and was implemented on January 1, 2010.

00:16:36.159 --> 00:16:37.159
That's great! Awesome, awesome, awesome.

00:16:37.320 --> 00:16:37.679
Bye-bye.

00:16:37.919 --> 00:16:39.039
Be careful.

00:16:39.960 --> 00:16:41.039
Remember to eat your food.

00:16:41.039 --> 00:16:42.759
And remember to go to the bathroom before the exam.

00:16:43.720 --> 00:16:44.159
Come with me.

00:16:45.240 --> 00:16:46.559
Do you remember the you who loved photography,

00:16:46.919 --> 00:16:48.240
who once wanted to be a short video vlogger,

00:16:48.799 --> 00:16:50.440
and even went to the snow mountain behind Godmother's back?

00:16:51.879 --> 00:16:53.080
I am here to help you fulfill your wish.

00:16:54.120 --> 00:16:55.000
Isn't this camera mine?

00:16:55.080 --> 00:16:56.000
Don't worry about the details.

00:16:56.200 --> 00:16:56.519
Let's go.

00:16:57.000 --> 00:16:57.279
What for?

00:16:57.279 --> 00:16:57.519
Let's go.

00:16:57.679 --> 00:16:58.080
Where to?

00:16:58.519 --> 00:16:58.919
Just come on.

00:16:59.919 --> 00:17:00.919
What you see right now...

00:17:01.279 --> 00:17:02.720
is one of the items on your Bucket List.

00:17:03.519 --> 00:17:04.880
This is what I've carefully prepared for you:

00:17:04.880 --> 00:17:06.480
The Ultimate Junk Food Party.

